    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section id="about">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2>Welcome to India's Largest Booking Platform</h2>
            <p>At [Your Company Name], we pride ourselves on being one of India's largest booking platforms, dedicated
                to making travel and tour experiences seamless and unforgettable for our customers.</p>
            <p>Our platform offers an easy-to-use interface that allows users to browse and book a wide range of travel
                destinations and tour packages. Whether you're looking for a serene hill station, a vibrant city tour,
                or an adventurous trekking experience, we have something for everyone.</p>
            <p>In addition to providing a comprehensive booking service, we also offer opportunities for individuals and
                businesses to join us as tour organizers. By partnering with us, you can reach a wider audience and grow
                your travel business with ease.</p>

            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Vast Selection of Tours and Destinations:</strong> We offer a wide variety of tours and
                    destinations to cater to all kinds of travelers.</li>
                <li><strong>Easy Booking Process:</strong> Our platform is designed to provide a seamless booking
                    experience from start to finish.</li>
                <li><strong>Trusted by Thousands:</strong> We have built a reputation for reliability and trust, with
                    thousands of satisfied customers.</li>
                <li><strong>Join as a Tour Organizer:</strong> Expand your business by becoming a part of our growing
                    network of tour organizers.</li>
            </ol>

            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to make travel planning and booking as easy and enjoyable as possible. We aim to connect
                travelers with the best travel experiences and tour organizers, ensuring that every trip is a memorable
                one.</p>

            <h2>Steps to Join as a Tour Organizer</h2>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Sign Up:</strong> Create an account on our platform.</li>
                <li><strong>List Your Tours:</strong> Add details about the tours and experiences you offer.</li>
                <li><strong>Get Approved:</strong> Our team will review and approve your listings.</li>
                <li><strong>Start Receiving Bookings:</strong> Once approved, you can start receiving bookings from our
                    extensive user base.</li>
                <li><strong>Grow Your Business:</strong> Reach a larger audience and grow your business with our support
                    and resources.</li>
            </ol>

            <img src="your-image.jpg" alt="About Us Image">
        </div>
    </section>

